&lt;h2 id="the-video-game"&gt;The video game&lt;a class="headerlink" href="#the-video-game" title="Permanent link"&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Game shares the Lego methodology for other games: pickup &lt;code&gt;coins&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;break&lt;/code&gt;
objects to find more coins or things to &lt;code&gt;build&lt;/code&gt; for making progress in the game, but
also combined with &lt;code&gt;special abilities&lt;/code&gt; like some objects being only
&lt;code&gt;breakable&lt;/code&gt; by specific characters, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If a character is required but not owned, it’s possible to &lt;code&gt;rent&lt;/code&gt; by using
some of the earned pieces that character for some time interval, allowing us
to complete certain tasks and keep progressing in the stories.&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="blog"></category><category term="Lego"></category><category term="Xbox"></category><category term="PlayStation"></category><category term="ps3"></category><category term="ps4"></category><category term="Wii"></category><category term="dimensions"></category><category term="NFS"></category><category term="review"></category></entry></feed>